guest_message: Hey! I'd like to place an order for a few items. Can I get a Caesar Salad with salmon, dressing on the side, and no croutons? Also, a Vegetable Stir Fry with tofu, brown rice, and mild spice. Lastly, a Portobello Mushroom Burger with vegan cheese and a side salad. Could you also let me know the total price for these? Thanks!
Sure thing! The name for the order is Barbara Nelson. I'll skip the drink, thanks. Everything else looks perfect.
